# EUCS IDAM End User Guidance

This is the home page of the **EUCS IDAM End User Guidance**. Here you will find user guides, advice, IdAM policies and signage to raise requests and quiries.

## How To Raise A Requst

For any quiries that do not match the below requests, please contact us at **[EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk)**

| Request Type | Task | How To Raise The Request |
| ----------- | ----------- | ----------- |
| Account Management | Add User account (MOJO - Production) | [New User Account](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=7404ac3137b723005f7cd1b543990e3e&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Delete User account (MOJO - Production) | [Delete User Account](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=c195e78edb73e7441b4ffc45ae9619f2&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Request Service Account (MOJO - Production) | TBD |
| | Add/Remove Guest Account (MOJO - Production) | Email IdAM team [EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Add/Remove Privileged Account (MOJO - LIVE, NLE an/or DEV) | [Add/Remove Privileged Account](https://mojprod.service-now.com/moj_sp?id=sc_cat_item&table=sc_cat_item&sys_id=8161246a1b170a50a1e2ddf0b24bcbdb&searchTerm=SERVICE%20ACCOUNT) |
| | Add/Remove Privileged Account (DOM1 - Dev) | Email IdAM team [EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Add/Remove Privileged Account (DOM1- NLE) | Email IdAM team [EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk) | 
| Application Consent | Delegated application consent approval | This should be requested via a demand so it can be reviewed formally before it is approved to agree that there is valid business justification. [Demand Guidance](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
| Security Group  | Add user | The owner of the group can perform these tasks (add/remove user). If owner not available then Email IdAM team [EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Remove User | The owner of the group can perform these tasks (add/remove user). If owner not available then Email IdAM team [EUCS IDAM Team Shared Inbox](mailto:idamteam@justice.gov.uk) |
| | Create new Security Group | IDAM can create the group. It is a demand request. [Demand Guidance](https://justiceuk.sharepoint.com/sites/DemandandBusinessRelationshipManagement/SitePages/New-Demand-Request.aspx) |
